com.tikal.jenkins.plugins.multijob.Multi.description:
Daily rebooting arrangement to ensure a clear test environment: - Revo2 VM powers off at 20:00 - Revo2 VM powers on at 20:20 - Jenkins server (pek-testharness-s1.wrs.com) reboots at 20:30 - Night test runs at 21:00 for ci spin
- Revo2 VM powers off at 01:00 - Revo2 VM powers on at 01:20 - Jenkins server (pek-testharness-s1.wrs.com) reboots at 01:30 - Night test runs at 02:00 for release spin ( previously run vx7-net branch)
